<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This book is a ride. A front-row seat to the inside of the LSD movement in the 60&apos;s. This book is fascinating to me from a historical perspective, thi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This book is a ride. A front-row seat to the inside of the LSD movement in the 60's. This book is fascinating to me from a historical perspective, this first-person account of a truly interesting time. It's also written in an unusual manner, not dry at all.. very psychedelic like Oisín said and full of popular slang of the day.<br /><br />Anyone who has an interest in the LSD movement of the 60's would find this book great reading, I'd think.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
